Package com.aheaditec.apdu.callbacks

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BasicCallback
    Basic callbacks which is extended by every callback.
    ByteArrayCallback
    This callback is used with ApduProvider.getCardID(ByteArrayCallback) and ApduProvider.signData(ContainerBasic, byte[], AlgorithmID, SignatureCallback) methods to get result in form of byte array.
    CertificateCallback
    Callback for ApduProvider.getCertificate(ContainerBasic, CertificateCallback) method.
    ContainerListCallback
    Callback for ApduProvider.getContainerList(ContainerListCallback) method.
    EmptyCallback
    This callback is used for methods which don't return specific response.
    InitializeCallback
    Callback used during initialization of SDK.
    PinInfoCallback
    Callback for ApduProvider.getPinInfo(VerifyCodes, PinInfoCallback) method.
    PinReferenceCallback
    Callback passing reference to a
    PublicKeyCallback
    Callback for ApduProvider.getPublicKey(ContainerBasic, PublicKeyCallback) method.
    SignatureCallback
    This callback is used with ApduProvider.signData(ContainerBasic, byte[], AlgorithmID, SignatureCallback) method to get signature in form of byte array.
    SignatureContinueCallback
    This callback is used only with SignatureCallback.onVerificationNeeded(VerifyCodes, SignatureContinueCallback) when the verification is required.
    VerifyCallback
    This callback is used together with ApduProvider.verify(VerifyCodes, byte[], boolean, VerifyCallback) method.
    VerifySignatureCallback
    Callback used at the end of verification of signature during ApduProvider.verifySignature(ContainerBasic, AlgorithmID, byte[], byte[], VerifySignatureCallback) method.
